---
description: Firebase integration rules.
globs:
  - "lib/**/*.dart"
  - "firebase/**/*"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Firebase

- Keep Firebase wrappers in `lib/core/services/`.
- Keep collection path constants in `lib/core/constants/firestore_paths.dart`.
- Do not access Firestore directly from widgets.
- Update `firebase/firestore.rules` and `firebase/firestore.indexes.json` with schema changes.
- Keep generated options in `lib/firebase_options.dart`.
